data.description: Modern convenience and attention to detail on display throughout this 4 bedroom 2 bath charmer. Entering this cozy and inviting home, you'll find modern updates and thoughtful upgrades including kitchen cabinets, back-splash, flooring, counter-tops, windows, fridge, dishwasher, gas stove/oven, laundry area, landscaping, central AC and heating! Entertain friends and family in the re-designed backyard with a built-in fire pit. This home also features a dog run, carport, and large backyard shed that could be used for extra storage purposes, media/work station, or even a private home gym/workout area! Great location with nearby shopping, schools, restaurants, freeway access and more. No HOA!
